# ================================
# NOTES FOR CONTRIBUTORS
# ================================
# If you need to add a file that's normally ignored:
# Use: git add -f filename
# 
# To see what files are being ignored:
# Use: git status --ignored
#
# To temporarily disable .gitignore:
# Use: git add -A (but be careful!)
#
# Remember to never commit:
# - Real bot tokens
# - Database files with user data  
# - Log files with sensitive information
# - Any credentials or API keys
